                    <value>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;TO CREATE A PAYMENT OFFER FOR SHIPMENT COSTS, PLEASE NOTE THE FOLLOWING INFORMATION:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;1. Add costs to payment request:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;The system will find all Billing records in the system that satisfy the following conditions:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Payment to in Billing = Payment to in payment request&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Both Available for PR (VND) and Available for PR (USD) information fields must be greater than 0. (If one of the two information fields is less than 0, it cannot be added to Payment Request)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;2. Add revenue to payment request for deduction:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;The system will find all Billing records in the system that satisfy the following conditions:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Invoice to in Billing = Payment to in payment request&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Both Available for deduction (VND) and Available for deduction (USD) fields must be greater than 0. (If one of the two information fields is less than 0, it cannot be added to Payment Request)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;</value>
